{"type": "article", "id": 4091, "title": "iPhone 扩音器 Ovo", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-04T08:30:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233358CM46Y3EJ81SagkKo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利品牌  Monitillo Marmi 日前邀请了来自米兰的设计工作室 May Day Design ，联手为 iPhone 设计了一款艺术感极强的扩音器 Ovo ，以大理石为原材料，通过精密的打磨与切割工艺，设计为一个圆筒的形状，并设置了专门放置 iPhone 的底部凹槽，将其放入扩音器中，便可以起到扩大音效的作用，即便不使用时，摆放在桌面上的 Ovo 也可以作为装饰品使用。定价 350 欧元<a href=\"http://www.lovethesign.com/brand/monitillo-marmi\" target=\"_blank\">，点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052333569KGZcq2EPUoh0Lm6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233356bPiFSyZG6sJVLKo1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233357U1oZRLw3jeQ8TAdH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233357MW3q4JhtFugNHKQI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233357No1tkT4M5r9unwmv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}